{"tid":2492879,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕人的第一部開篷車，五菱宏光 MINI EV CABRIO，5萬有交易？","createTime":"2021-04-17T12:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:00:30.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"893ec7bb042ce4d86db16f593de927cc4c2a6b72","tid":2492879,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbiPK1uKVF27GsMoPx352eBMVfDDe1pxnfeZ1dQZQGDh5?filename=aLvJwkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLvJwkh.png&h=28fba520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUjtLTyaBZndbckxU1MkFdyUbB17ruJnNQUEF2B6uCxSq?filename=yqcvVNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqcvVNJ.jpg&h=25b98b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaGMwu1KxDyCEmYA9Dr7CxxvqqnfiAQAUkmtVAnqkUKZo?filename=2G1sX04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2G1sX04.jpg&h=b2c1b642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國的五菱宏光 MINI EV 憑藉小巧的身材、親民的售價等優點，深受消費者的喜愛。上市僅僅200多天時間，五菱宏光 MINI EV 銷量就已經突破了20萬輛，是名副其實的「人民代步車」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n年輕人的第一部開篷車，五菱宏光 MINI EV CABRIO，5萬有交易？<br />\nBy Marco - 4 月 15, 2021<br />\n<br />\n中國的五菱宏光 MINI EV 憑藉小巧的身材、親民的售價等優點，深受消費者的喜愛。上市僅僅200多天時間，五菱宏光 MINI EV 銷量就已經突破了20萬輛，是名副其實的「人民代步車」。<br />\n<br />\n在五菱宏光 MINI EV 之後，五菱還推出了一款五菱宏光 MINI EV 馬卡龍，預售14天的訂單就突破了3.6萬輛，熱情依舊不減。<br />\n<br />\n在4月14日，五菱發布了五菱宏光 MINI EV 的新款車型&mdash;&mdash;五菱宏光 MINI EV CABRIO，並配上了官圖。從官圖中可以看到，該車是基於普通款車型打造，採用了開篷的結構，非常威水，將會在2021中國上海車展上進行亮相。<br />\n<br />\n外觀細節方面，五菱宏光 MINI EV 開篷版的車身周圍增加了不少與車身不同色的裝飾條，其車頭為銀色徽標，前保險槓造型更加簡約，看起來更加的時尚。<br />\n<br />\n最大的亮點在​​於採用了電動軟頂開篷機構，增加獨立的防滾架，在收起之後基本與車身持平。小巧迷你的車身，加上開篷設計，開在路上回頭率槓槓的。<br />\n<br />\n內櫳方面，開篷版車型進行了重新設計，改為簡潔的白灰色主題和雙10吋大連屏，軚盤變成了平底設計，整體看起來更加「運動」。<br />\n<br />\n性能方面，開篷版將沿用現款車型的動力組合，其電機最大功率為20kW，峰值扭矩85N&middot;m。提供 NEDC 120km 和 170km 兩種續航版本供消費者進行選擇。<br />\n<br />\n售價方面，剛上市的五菱宏光 MINI EV 馬卡龍售價為3.76-4.36萬元人民幣，開篷版車型肯定會超過普通版車型，估計5萬元人民幣左右。"},{"pid":"c94a48c812539765ed2d4cf66d9db620283eee91","tid":2492879,"uid":12252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:35:43.000Z","msg":"柒撚到 送都唔撚渣"},{"pid":"73adbef63c35ee6f47e510592efe7c5dd569dd73","tid":2492879,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"c0188cb47d71e6c2edc42e8d750beb39358edb2a","tid":2492879,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"玩具反斗城幾百蚊都有啦 一樣係電動"},{"pid":"d983a83cb3fbec53bcd2f762826748b8612daaa3","tid":2492879,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma6v1iXKRToykpTadmZn1DdHvxNNTRf1NgCJemCLg98jp?filename=uuR8HuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuuR8HuD.jpg&h=44cec574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b119fb6f47fe408dfe39fa8245a504587b1cb717","tid":2492879,"uid":5597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"揸出街比人笑到面都黃 大陸狗都唔揸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1035591a290c56fa1536af433fdf5a4795fce7","tid":2492879,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"好chill"},{"pid":"bcd26da5ab55d340356e23332476083d5a4ecfe8","tid":2492879,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"仲開篷<br />\n驚死得唔夠快?"}]}